==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Twaite
<hw>Twaite</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(O. Eng. Law)</fld> <def>A piece of
cleared ground. See <er>Thwaite</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

